{"tid":543686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚇一跳】天文台App出錯 顯示明晚8點跌穿-1°C","createTime":"2018-01-28T17:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T20:51:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c2faee97da3a09977197dbaf2f82cef9a856d8","tid":543686,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180128/large/1517129955_96a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180128%2Flarge%2F1517129955_96a6.jpg&h=43f64f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【16:45更新】天文台在官方網頁中表示，由於系統故障，「自動分區天氣預報」中的1月29日（星期一）天文台總部氣溫預測曾顯示錯誤數據。經搶修後現已回復正常。天文台會繼續留意情況。<br />\n<br />\n寒冷天氣警告現正生效。天文台表示，一道冷鋒正橫過珠江口一帶，受隨後的強烈冬季季候風影響，本港今晚氣溫開始驟降，跌至明日最低的9&deg;C。不過，天文台的iPhone手機應用程式懷疑出錯，今午更新的數據顯示明晚8時本港氣溫將會跌至驚人的-1&deg;C，並在3個小時後回升至19&deg;C，不但跌穿冰點，溫差更加勁過玩「跳樓機」。<br />\n至於天文台的網頁則未有變化，顯示本周天氣持續寒冷，最低氣溫普遍在9&deg;C左右，最寒冷的兩天，市區氣溫仍只是低見8&deg;C。<br />\n天文台在官方網頁中表示，由於系統故障，「自動分區天氣預報」中的1月29日（星期一）天文台總部氣溫預測曾顯示錯誤數據。經搶修後現已回復正常。天文台會繼續留意情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180128/57764000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57764000&d=9YKHrMJwdctXi9TL31ylgJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=d6b0da45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57764000&h=48ba7ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180128/57764000</a>"},{"pid":"4f09b3da484ff4f55c2e35c07a5d10d33353968d","tid":543686,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"dc98e3818bf89399b37837e7f438b6d31d4ccc11","tid":543686,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T18:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gi